{"{\"query\":\"query ListAnime ($page: Int, $search: String, $perPage: Int, $sort: [MediaSort], $status: [MediaStatus], $genres: [String], $averageScore_greater: Int, $season: MediaSeason, $seasonYear: Int, $format: MediaFormat, $isAdult: Boolean) {\\n\\tPage(page: $page, perPage: $perPage) {\\n\\t\\tpageInfo {\\n\\t\\t\\thasNextPage\\n\\t\\t\\ttotal\\n\\t\\t\\tperPage\\n\\t\\t\\tcurrentPage\\n\\t\\t\\tlastPage\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t\\tmedia(type: ANIME, search: $search, sort: $sort, status_in: $status, isAdult: $isAdult, format: $format, genre_in: $genres, averageScore_greater: $averageScore_greater, season: $season, seasonYear: $seasonYear, format_not: MUSIC) {\\n\\t\\t\\t... baseAnime\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t}\\n}\\nfragment baseAnime on Media {\\n\\tid\\n\\tidMal\\n\\tsiteUrl\\n\\tstatus(version: 2)\\n\\tseason\\n\\ttype\\n\\tformat\\n\\tseasonYear\\n\\tbannerImage\\n\\tepisodes\\n\\tsynonyms\\n\\tisAdult\\n\\tcountryOfOrigin\\n\\tmeanScore\\n\\tdescription\\n\\tgenres\\n\\tduration\\n\\ttrailer {\\n\\t\\tid\\n\\t\\tsite\\n\\t\\tthumbnail\\n\\t}\\n\\ttitle {\\n\\t\\tuserPreferred\\n\\t\\tromaji\\n\\t\\tenglish\\n\\t\\tnative\\n\\t}\\n\\tcoverImage {\\n\\t\\textraLarge\\n\\t\\tlarge\\n\\t\\tmedium\\n\\t\\tcolor\\n\\t}\\n\\tstartDate {\\n\\t\\tyear\\n\\t\\tmonth\\n\\t\\tday\\n\\t}\\n\\tendDate {\\n\\t\\tyear\\n\\t\\tmonth\\n\\t\\tday\\n\\t}\\n\\tnextAiringEpisode {\\n\\t\\tairingAt\\n\\t\\ttimeUntilAiring\\n\\t\\tepisode\\n\\t}\\n}\\n\",\"variables\":{\"format\":\"MOVIE\",\"isAdult\":false,\"page\":1,\"perPage\":20,\"sort\":[\"TRENDING_DESC\"],\"status\":[\"RELEASING\",\"FINISHED\"]}}":{"value":{"Page":{"media":[{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/178788-tSHb5MiaNBNL.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#35bbe4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx178788-zm3gtpB9TpRt.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx178788-zm3gtpB9TpRt.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx178788-zm3gtpB9TpRt.jpg"},"description":"\u003ci\u003ePart 1 of the theatrical trilogy adaptation of the Infinity Castle Arc.\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nTanjiro Kamado – a boy who joined an organization dedicated to hunting down demons called the Demon Slayer Corps after his younger sister Nezuko was turned into a demon.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nWhile growing stronger and deepening his friendships and bonds with fellow corps members, Tanjiro has battled many demons with his comrades – Zenitsu Agatsuma and Inosuke Hashibira. Along the way, his journey has led him to fight alongside the Demon Slayer Corps’ highest-ranking swordsmen, the Hashira, including Flame Hashira Kyojuro Rengoku aboard the Mugen Train, Sound Hashira Tengen Uzui within the Entertainment District, as well as Mist Hashira Muichiro Tokito and Love Hashira Mitsuri Kanroji at the Swordsmith Village.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAs the Demon Slayer Corps members and Hashira engaged in a group strength training program, the Hashira Training, in preparation for the forthcoming battle against the demons, Muzan Kibutsuji appears at the Ubuyashiki Mansion. With the head of the Demon Corps in danger, Tanjiro and the Hashira rush to the headquarters but are plunged into a deep descent to a mysterious space by the hands of Muzan Kibutsuji.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThe destination of where Tanjiro and Demon Slayer Corps have fallen is the demons’ stronghold – the Infinity Castle. And so, the battleground is set as the final battle between the Demon Slayer Corps and the demons ignites.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":155,"endDate":{"day":18,"month":7,"year":2025},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Drama","Fantasy","Supernatural"],"id":178788,"idMal":59192,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":87,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2025,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/178788","startDate":{"day":18,"month":7,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba La Forteresse infinie","Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Castelo Infinito","Клинок, Рассекающий Демонов: Бесконечный Замок"],"title":{"english":"Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle","native":"劇場版「鬼滅の刃」無限城編 第一章 猗窩座再来","romaji":"Kimetsu no Yaiba: Mugenjou-hen Movie 1 - Akaza Sairai","userPreferred":"Kimetsu no Yaiba: Mugenjou-hen Movie 1 - Akaza Sairai"},"trailer":{"id":"ZfIXXgqxVn8","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ZfIXXgqxVn8/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/171627-7esVHhgw69rn.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e43550","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx171627-ZN9D7P46yHnw.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx171627-ZN9D7P46yHnw.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx171627-ZN9D7P46yHnw.png"},"description":"Theatrical follow-up to \u003ci\u003eChainsaw Man\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nDenji became “Chainsaw Man”, a boy with a devil’s heart, and is now part of Special Division 4’s devil hunters. After a date with Makima, the woman of his dreams, Denji takes shelter from the rain. There he meets Reze, a girl who works in a café.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: MAPPA CHANNEL)\n\n","duration":100,"endDate":{"day":19,"month":9,"year":2025},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Drama","Horror","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":171627,"idMal":57555,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":90,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2025,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/171627","startDate":{"day":19,"month":9,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["CSM: Reze-hen","CSM – The Movie: Reze Arc","Chainsaw Man – O Filme: Arco da Reze","Chainsaw Man - La película: El arco de Reze","Chainsaw Man - Il Film: La Storia di Reze","Человек-бензопила: Фильм – История Резе"],"title":{"english":"Chainsaw Man – The Movie: Reze Arc","native":"チェンソーマン レゼ篇","romaji":"Chainsaw Man: Reze-hen","userPreferred":"Chainsaw Man: Reze-hen"},"trailer":{"id":"pv8A7eubPQQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pv8A7eubPQQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/177687-24ePtQwAUb7n.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e46b5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx177687-T4SrtVjrmW01.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx177687-T4SrtVjrmW01.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx177687-T4SrtVjrmW01.png"},"description":"\u003ci\u003e100 METERS\u003c/i\u003e follows Togashi, a track star who is born to run. As a kid, he is naturally gifted and wins every 100-meter race without effort. But in sixth grade, he meets Komiya, a transfer student who is full of determination but lacks technique. In teaching him, Togashi gives Komiya a new purpose: to win no matter what. Years pass by, and Togashi and Komiya meet again as rivals on the track and reveal their true selves.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: GKIDS)","duration":106,"endDate":{"day":19,"month":9,"year":2025},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Drama","Sports"],"id":177687,"idMal":58919,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2025,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/177687","startDate":{"day":19,"month":9,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["100M","A Corrida dos 100 Metros","100 metros lisos","100 Mètres"],"title":{"english":"100 METERS","native":"ひゃくえむ。","romaji":"Hyakuemu.","userPreferred":"Hyakuemu."},"trailer":{"id":"oXeYSCXSFhs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/oXeYSCXSFhs/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/20954-f30bHMXa5Qoe.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5dbbe4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx20954-sYRfE5jQRtSB.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx20954-sYRfE5jQRtSB.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx20954-sYRfE5jQRtSB.jpg"},"description":"After transferring into a new school, a deaf girl, Shouko Nishimiya, is bullied by the popular Shouya Ishida. As Shouya continues to bully Shouko, the class turns its back on him. Shouko transfers and Shouya grows up as an outcast. Alone and depressed, the regretful Shouya finds Shouko to make amends.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Eleven Arts)","duration":130,"endDate":{"day":17,"month":9,"year":2016},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":20954,"idMal":28851,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":88,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2016,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/20954","startDate":{"day":17,"month":9,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["The Shape of Voice","A Voz do Silêncio","A Forma da Voz","La Forma della Voce","צורתו של קול","声之形","الحزن الصامت","Una voz silenciosa","La Forme de la voix","Форма голоса","Форма голосу","Tylus balsas","Balss forma","Дауыс пішіні","Sakit səs","รักไร้เสียง"],"title":{"english":"A Silent Voice","native":"聲の形","romaji":"Koe no Katachi","userPreferred":"Koe no Katachi"},"trailer":{"id":"Sy4bPCuzfiQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Sy4bPCuzfiQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/131573-3veuVz5p0z2I.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c95d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx131573-rpl82vDEDRm6.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx131573-rpl82vDEDRm6.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx131573-rpl82vDEDRm6.jpg"},"description":"Yuta Okkotsu is a nervous high school student who is suffering from a serious problem—his childhood friend Rika has turned into a curse and won't leave him alone. Since Rika is no ordinary curse, his plight is noticed by Satoru Gojo, a teacher at Jujutsu High, a school where fledgling exorcists learn how to combat curses. Gojo convinces Yuta to enroll, but can he learn enough in time to confront the curse that haunts him?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: VIZ Media)","duration":105,"endDate":{"day":24,"month":12,"year":2021},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Supernatural"],"id":131573,"idMal":48561,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2021,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/131573","startDate":{"day":24,"month":12,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["JJK 0","咒术回战0","มหาเวทย์ผนึกมาร : ซีโร่","‎جوجوتسو كايسن 0","Jujutsu Kaisen Movie","Магическая битва 0"],"title":{"english":"JUJUTSU KAISEN 0","native":"呪術廻戦 0","romaji":"Jujutsu Kaisen 0","userPreferred":"Jujutsu Kaisen 0"},"trailer":{"id":"2docezZl574","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2docezZl574/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/198188-rIqUa8loin9T.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4d650","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx198188-h3w6uICVNhqh.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx198188-h3w6uICVNhqh.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx198188-h3w6uICVNhqh.png"},"description":"An anthology series adapting 8 short stories created by manga artist Tatsuki Fujimoto between ages 17 and 26.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n1) \u003ci\u003eA Couple Clucking Chickens Were Still Kickin' in the Schoolyard\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Seishirou Nagaya, ZEXCS)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n2) \u003ci\u003eSasaki Stopped a Bullet\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Nobukage Kimura, Lapin Track)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n3) \u003ci\u003eLove is Blind\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Nobuyuki Takeuchi, Lapin Track)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n4) \u003ci\u003eShikaku\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Naoya Ando, GRAPH77)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n5) \u003ci\u003eMermaid Rhapsody\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Tetsuaki Watanabe, 100Studio)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n6) \u003ci\u003eWoke-Up-as-a-Girl Syndrome\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Kazuaki Terasawa, Studio Kafka)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n7) \u003ci\u003eNayuta of the Prophecy\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Tetsuaki Watanabe, 100Studio)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n8) \u003ci\u003eSisters\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Osamu Honma, P.A.WORKS)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: This anime had a pre-release world premiere at the \"Global Stage Hollywood 2025\" film festival on October 5, 2025. A general two-week theatrical run in Japan divided into two parts released on the same day October 17, 2025. The anime series later streamed worldwide in Amazon Prime Video on November 8, 2025.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":18,"endDate":{"day":17,"month":10,"year":2025},"episodes":8,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Comedy","Drama","Romance","Sci-Fi","Slice of Life","Supernatural"],"id":198188,"idMal":62405,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2025,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/198188","startDate":{"day":17,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["A Couple Clucking Chickens Were Still Kickin' in the Schoolyard","Sasaki Stopped a Bullet","Love is Blind","Shikaku","Mermaid Rhapsody","Woke-Up-as-a-Girl Syndrome","Nayuta of the Prophecy","Sisters"," 庭には二羽 ニワトリがいた。","佐々木くんが 銃弾止めた","恋は盲目","シカク","人魚ラプソディ","目が覚めたら 女の子になっていた病 ","予言のナユタ","妹の姉"],"title":{"english":"Tatsuki Fujimoto 17-26","native":"藤本タツキ 17-26","romaji":"Fujimoto Tatsuki 17-26","userPreferred":"Fujimoto Tatsuki 17-26"},"trailer":{"id":"xDsN2cmAlhQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/xDsN2cmAlhQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/142770-YgESt2HJXlNg.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#43bbe4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx142770-dDaDIRnsv5jN.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx142770-dDaDIRnsv5jN.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx142770-dDaDIRnsv5jN.jpg"},"description":"The story follows Suzume, a 17-year-old girl from a quiet Kyushu town who meets a young man looking for a door. They find a door within ruins in the mountain, and Suzume opens it. Soon, more doors begin to open around Japan, bringing disasters from the other side. The film depicts Suzume's liberation and growth, as she closes the doors that are causing disaster.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":121,"endDate":{"day":11,"month":11,"year":2022},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Adventure","Fantasy","Mystery","Supernatural"],"id":142770,"idMal":50594,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2022,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/142770","startDate":{"day":11,"month":11,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["铃芽之旅","Khóa Chặt Cửa Nào Suzume","การผนึกประตูของซุซุเมะ","Судзуме зачиняє двері","Судзумэ"],"title":{"english":"Suzume","native":"すずめの戸締まり","romaji":"Suzume no Tojimari","userPreferred":"Suzume no Tojimari"},"trailer":{"id":"g0JMPkn7Wuo","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/g0JMPkn7Wuo/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/112151-eHCBz19nf2yC.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5dc9f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx112151-1qlQwPB1RrJe.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx112151-1qlQwPB1RrJe.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx112151-1qlQwPB1RrJe.png"},"description":"This Demon Slayer movie sees Tanjiro Kamado and friends from the Demon Slayer corps board the Infinity Train on a new mission to investigate a mysterious series of disappearances, perpetrated by a demon who has been tormenting people and killing the demon slayers who oppose it.","duration":117,"endDate":{"day":16,"month":10,"year":2020},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Drama","Fantasy","Mystery","Supernatural"],"id":112151,"idMal":40456,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2020,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/112151","startDate":{"day":16,"month":10,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["KnY Movie","Els Guardians de la Nit: El Tren Infinit","Guardianes de la Noche: Tren Infinito","Demon Slayer: Mugen Treni","Demon Slayer: Il Treno Mugen","鬼灭之刃：无限列车篇","قاتل الشياطين الفيلم: قطار اللانهاية","ดาบพิฆาตอสูร เดอะมูฟวี่ : ศึกรถไฟสู่นิรันดร์","Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - Le film : Le train de l'Infini","ΚΥΝΗΓΟΣ ΔΑΙΜΟΝΩΝ: KIMETSU NO YAIBA – Η ΤΑΙΝΙΑ: ΤΟ ΤΡΕΝΟ ΜΟΥΓΚΕΝ","극장판 귀멸의 칼날: 무한열차편","Клинок, Рассекающий Демонов: Бесконечный Поезд"],"title":{"english":"Demon Slayer -Kimetsu no Yaiba- The Movie: Mugen Train","native":"鬼滅の刃 無限列車編","romaji":"Kimetsu no Yaiba: Mugen Ressha-hen","userPreferred":"Kimetsu no Yaiba: Mugen Ressha-hen"},"trailer":{"id":"23riEOmDOgM","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/23riEOmDOgM/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/164-Aj6MINy7VTfs.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx164-ySuGzCWVw2cL.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx164-ySuGzCWVw2cL.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx164-ySuGzCWVw2cL.jpg"},"description":"A calm village residing in the mountains comes under attack from a demon-possessed boar one day.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAshitaka, a young man and prince of the tribe, engages the creature in an attempt to save his village. During the battle, the boar bites him on the arm, leaving it blackened and cursed. Following his village's traditions, Ashitaka is exiled and becomes a wanderer, looking for a solution to the curse before it engulfs him.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nIron Town is a fortress under the leadership of Lady Eboshi. Through the clearing of the surrounding forests, Iron Town produces large amounts of Ironsand, used for gunpowder and other machinery. However, because of the forests destruction, nearby animal clans seek revenge led by a human girl of the Wolf clan called San.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nWhen Ashitaka comes to Iron Town, he discovers the area consumed in battle. Horrified, he attempts to create peace and befriend the Wolf Clan. However, after the forest's eradication and the ongoing war between Human and Beast, will the Spirit of the Forest be forgiving and accept Ashitaka's request to expel his curse?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]","duration":134,"endDate":{"day":12,"month":7,"year":1997},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":164,"idMal":164,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":1997,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/164","startDate":{"day":12,"month":7,"year":1997},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["La Princesa Mononoke","Księżniczka Mononoke","Principessa Mononoke","الأميرة مونونوكي","Prenses Mononoke","Princesse Mononoké","Princesa Mononoke","A Princesa Mononoke","Prinzessin Mononoke","Πριγκίπισσα Μονονόκε","Prinsessan Mononoke","Prinsesse Mononoke","Mononoke Prinsessa"],"title":{"english":"Princess Mononoke","native":"もののけ姫","romaji":"Mononoke-hime","userPreferred":"Mononoke-hime"},"trailer":{"id":"4OiMOHRDs14","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/4OiMOHRDs14/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/174788-0ZM9g7npJH8X.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx174788-9LsUnn0oEppv.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx174788-9LsUnn0oEppv.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx174788-9LsUnn0oEppv.jpg"},"description":"Ayumu Fujino is a fourth grader who draws a manga strip for the school newspaper. Her art makes her the star of the class, but one day she's told that Kyomoto, a student who refuses to come to school, would also like to submit a manga for the paper...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: MANGA Plus, edited)","duration":58,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":6,"year":2024},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Drama","Slice of Life"],"id":174788,"idMal":58125,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":86,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2024,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/174788","startDate":{"day":28,"month":6,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"LOOK BACK","native":"ルックバック","romaji":"Look Back","userPreferred":"Look Back"},"trailer":{"id":"H6HOnlTnVwc","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/H6HOnlTnVwc/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/142769-WCECHopEFbE2.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#28c9e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx142769-kNyyqpwC9gGV.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx142769-kNyyqpwC9gGV.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx142769-kNyyqpwC9gGV.jpg"},"description":"Urashima Tunnel - Once you enter that tunnel, you can get whatever you want, but at a price. Kaoru Tohno, who seems to have an elusive personality and traumatic past, and Anzu Hanashiro, who is struggling to reconcile her ideal image and true-to-heart attitude, team up to investigate the Urashima Tunnel and get what they want. This is an unforgettable summer story of nostalgia and sprinting in a remote countryside.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: HIDIVE)","duration":83,"endDate":{"day":9,"month":9,"year":2022},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Drama","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":142769,"idMal":50593,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2022,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/142769","startDate":{"day":9,"month":9,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["คำจากลาของคิมหันต์ ณ ปลายอุโมงค์","Natsuton","El túnel de los deseos"],"title":{"english":"The Tunnel to Summer, the Exit of Goodbyes","native":"夏へのトンネル、さよならの出口","romaji":"Natsu e no Tunnel, Sayonara no Deguchi","userPreferred":"Natsu e no Tunnel, Sayonara no Deguchi"},"trailer":{"id":"29KybHTiCqc","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/29KybHTiCqc/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/99750-KPFW2Jv03b2B.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c9f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx99750-pNyly9d3MEgV.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx99750-pNyly9d3MEgV.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx99750-pNyly9d3MEgV.jpg"},"description":"Spring time in April and the last of the cherry blossoms are still in bloom. The usually aloof bookworm with no interest in others comes across a book in a hospital waiting room. Handwritten on the cover are the words: \"Living with Dying.\" He soon discovers that it is a diary kept by his very popular and genuinely cheerful classmate, Sakura Yamauchi, who reveals to him that she is secretly suffering from a pancreatic illness and only has a limited time left. It is at this moment that she gains just one more person to share her secret.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nTrying to maintain a normal life as much as possible, Sakura is determined to live her life to the fullest until the very last day. As her free spirit and unpredictable actions throw him for a loop, his heart begins to gradually change.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Aniplex USA)","duration":108,"endDate":{"day":1,"month":9,"year":2018},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":99750,"idMal":36098,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2018,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/99750","startDate":{"day":1,"month":9,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Quiero Comerme tu Páncreas","Voglio mangiare il tuo pancreas","Je veux manger ton pancréas","Vull menjar-me el teu pàncrees","Kimisui","Eu Quero Comer Seu Pâncreas","Хочу съесть твою поджелудочную железу","ตับอ่อนเธอนั้นขอฉันเถอะนะ"],"title":{"english":"I Want to Eat Your Pancreas","native":"君の膵臓をたべたい","romaji":"Kimi no Suizou wo Tabetai","userPreferred":"Kimi no Suizou wo Tabetai"},"trailer":{"id":"MmoBvmJA9XI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MmoBvmJA9XI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21519-1ayMXgNlmByb.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#0da1e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx21519-SUo3ZQuCbYhJ.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx21519-SUo3ZQuCbYhJ.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx21519-SUo3ZQuCbYhJ.png"},"description":"Mitsuha Miyamizu, a high school girl, yearns to live the life of a boy in the bustling city of Tokyo—a dream that stands in stark contrast to her present life in the countryside. Meanwhile in the city, Taki Tachibana lives a busy life as a high school student while juggling his part-time job and hopes for a future in architecture.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nOne day, Mitsuha awakens in a room that is not her own and suddenly finds herself living the dream life in Tokyo—but in Taki's body! Elsewhere, Taki finds himself living Mitsuha's life in the humble countryside. In pursuit of an answer to this strange phenomenon, they begin to search for one another.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eKimi no Na wa.\u003c/i\u003e revolves around Mitsuha and Taki's actions, which begin to have a dramatic impact on each other's lives, weaving them into a fabric held together by fate and circumstance.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: MAL Rewrite)","duration":107,"endDate":{"day":26,"month":8,"year":2016},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Drama","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":21519,"idMal":32281,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2016,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21519","startDate":{"day":26,"month":8,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Your Name. - Gestern, heute und für immer ","Mi a Neved? ","你的名字。","너의 이름은.","Tu nombre","Твоё имя","หลับตาฝันถึงชื่อเธอ","Il tuo nome","השם שלך.","Twoje imię"],"title":{"english":"Your Name.","native":"君の名は。","romaji":"Kimi no Na wa.","userPreferred":"Kimi no Na wa."},"trailer":{"id":"k4xGqY5IDBE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/k4xGqY5IDBE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/199-Sm2RU5PSqw7T.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx199-sWefXJvXkDOb.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx199-sWefXJvXkDOb.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx199-sWefXJvXkDOb.jpg"},"description":"On the way to their new home, 10-year-old Chihiro Ogino's family stumbles upon a deserted theme park. Intrigued, the family investigates the park, though unbeknownst to them, it is secretly inhabited by spirits who sleep by day and appear at night. When Chihiro's mother and father eat food from a restaurant in the street, angry spirits turn them into pigs. Furthermore, a wide sea has appeared between the spirit world and the human one, trapping Chihiro, the sole human, in a land of spirits. Luckily for her though, a mysterious boy named Haku appears, claiming to know her from the past. Under his instructions, Chihiro secures a job in the bathhouse where Haku works. With only her courage and some new found friends to aid her, Chihiro embarks on a journey to turn her parents back to their original forms and return home.\n","duration":125,"endDate":{"day":20,"month":7,"year":2001},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Adventure","Drama","Fantasy","Supernatural"],"id":199,"idMal":199,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":86,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2001,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/199","startDate":{"day":20,"month":7,"year":2001},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Le Voyage de Chihiro","La Città Incantata","El Viaje de Chihiro","Chihiros Reise ins Zauberland","Ruhların Kaçışı","המסע המופלא","Călătoria lui Chihiro","Spirited Away: W krainie bogów","Chihiro Szellemországban","A Viagem de Chihiro","千与千寻","Унесённые призраками","Chihiro og heksene","Ταξίδι στην Χώρα των Θαυμάτων","มิติวิญญาณมหัศจรรย์","Henkien kätkemä","Chihiro ilmmiid gaskkas","Vaimudest viidud","Chihiro og álögin"],"title":{"english":"Spirited Away","native":"千と千尋の神隠し","romaji":"Sen to Chihiro no Kamikakushi","userPreferred":"Sen to Chihiro no Kamikakushi"},"trailer":{"id":"ByXuk9QqQkk","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ByXuk9QqQkk/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/133845-B5ztyViSVCQH.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e46b43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx133845-InD67nSzCAUr.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx133845-InD67nSzCAUr.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx133845-InD67nSzCAUr.png"},"description":"Theatrical follow-up to \u003ci\u003eOverlord IV\u003c/i\u003e. The film will cover the \"Holy Kingdom\" arc.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAfter twelve years of playing his favorite MMORPG game, Momonga logs in for the last time only to find himself transported into its world playing it indefinitely. Throughout his adventures, his avatar ascends to the title of Sorcerer King Ains Ooal Gown.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nOnce prosperous but now on the brink of ruin, The Sacred Kingdom enjoyed years of peace after construction of an enormous wall protecting them from neighboring invasions. But, one day this comes to an end when the Demon Emperor Jaldabaoth arrives with an army of villainous demi-humans. \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nFearing invasion of their own lands, the neighboring territory of the Slane Theocracy is forced to beg their enemies at the Sorcerer Kingdom for help. Heeding the call, Momonga, now known as the Sorcerer King Ains Ooal Gown, rallies the Sorcerer Kingdom and its undead army to join the fight alongside the Sacred Kingdom and the Slane Theocracy in hopes to defeat the Demon Emperor. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll, edited)","duration":135,"endDate":{"day":20,"month":9,"year":2024},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":133845,"idMal":48896,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2024,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/133845","startDate":{"day":20,"month":9,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Overlord Movie 3","Overlord: Holy Kingdom Arc","โอเวอร์ลอร์ด บทนครศักดิ์สิทธิ์","Overlord: The Paladin of the Sacred Kingdom Arc","Overlord: O Reino Sagrado","Overlord: El Reino Sagrado"],"title":{"english":"OVERLORD: The Sacred Kingdom","native":"オーバーロード 聖王国編","romaji":"Overlord: Sei Oukoku-hen","userPreferred":"Overlord: Sei Oukoku-hen"},"trailer":{"id":"vniS5g48wHA","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/vniS5g48wHA/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/113596-8r3fCSFgQHIY.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#a1e4ff","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx113596-LKA0bYJGjLnB.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx113596-LKA0bYJGjLnB.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx113596-LKA0bYJGjLnB.jpg"},"description":"The story centers on the relationship between Tsuneo and Josee. Tsuneo is a university student, and Josee is a young girl who has rarely gone out of the house by herself due to her being unable to walk. The two meet when Tsuneo finds Josee's grandmother taking her out for a morning walk.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":98,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":12,"year":2020},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":113596,"idMal":40787,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2020,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/113596","startDate":{"day":25,"month":12,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Josee to Tora to Sakana-tachi","乔西的虎与鱼","Josee, el Tigre y los Peces","Josee, El Tigre i Els Peixos","โจเซ่ กับเสือและหมู่ปลา","Josie, der Tiger und die Fische.","Josée, le tigre et les poissons","Её заветное желание","Жозе, тигр и рыба"," Josée, la Tigre e i Pesci"],"title":{"english":"Josee, the Tiger and the Fish","native":"ジョゼと虎と魚たち","romaji":"Josee to Tora to Sakanatachi","userPreferred":"Josee to Tora to Sakanatachi"},"trailer":{"id":"QvgpMxoyDds","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/QvgpMxoyDds/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/106286-3oKwiwjd7Wkm.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5dbbe4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx106286-5COcpd0J9VbL.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx106286-5COcpd0J9VbL.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx106286-5COcpd0J9VbL.png"},"description":"High school student Hodaka leaves his home on an isolated island and moves to Tokyo, but he immediately becomes broke. He lives his days in isolation, but finally finds a job as a writer for a shady occult magazine. After he starts his job, the weather has been rainy day after day. In a corner of the crowded and busy city, Hodaka meets a young woman named Hina. Due to certain circumstances, Hina and her younger brother live together, but have a cheerful and sturdy life. Hina also has a certain power: the power to stop the rain and clear the sky.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":115,"endDate":{"day":19,"month":7,"year":2019},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Drama","Romance","Slice of Life","Supernatural"],"id":106286,"idMal":38826,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2019,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/106286","startDate":{"day":19,"month":7,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["El Tiempo Contigo","Weathering With You - Das Mädchen, das die Sonne berührte","Les enfants du temps","O Tempo Com Você","天气之子","La ragazza del tempo","Дитя погоды"],"title":{"english":"Weathering With You","native":"天気の子","romaji":"Tenki no Ko","userPreferred":"Tenki no Ko"},"trailer":{"id":"Q6iK6DjV_iE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Q6iK6DjV_iE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/104157-PS7tfPpvJKhk.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#8643f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx104157-rk99XI56PaIC.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx104157-rk99XI56PaIC.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx104157-rk99XI56PaIC.jpg"},"description":"In Fujisawa, where the skies are bright and the seas glisten, Sakuta Azusagawa is in his second year of high school. His blissful days with his girlfriend and upperclassman, Mai Sakurajima, are interrupted with the appearance of his first crush, Shouko Makinohara. For reasons unknown, he encounters two Shouko's: one in middle school and another who has become an adult.\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nAs Sakuta finds himself helplessly living with the Shouko's, the adult Shouko leads him around by the nose, causing a huge rift in his relationship with Mai.\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nIn the midst of all of this, he discovers that the middle school Shouko is suffering from a grave illness and his scar begins to throb...\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Aniplex USA)","duration":90,"endDate":{"day":15,"month":6,"year":2019},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Drama","Psychological","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":104157,"idMal":38329,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2019,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/104157","startDate":{"day":15,"month":6,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["青ブタ","Ao Buta ","青春猪头少年不会梦到怀梦美少女","Этот глупый свин не понимает мечту девочки-зайки. Фильм","Негодник, которому не снилась девушка-кролик. Фильм"],"title":{"english":"Rascal Does Not Dream of a Dreaming Girl","native":"青春ブタ野郎はゆめみる少女の夢を見ない","romaji":"Seishun Buta Yarou wa Yumemiru Shoujo no Yume wo Minai","userPreferred":"Seishun Buta Yarou wa Yumemiru Shoujo no Yume wo Minai"},"trailer":{"id":"UbLBbxSm8hs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/UbLBbxSm8hs/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101231-QB3E5LNZUPYg.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx101231-8X1CanhPk9iw.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx101231-8X1CanhPk9iw.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx101231-8X1CanhPk9iw.jpg"},"description":"Anthology film for three short stories. \u003cbr\u003e \nThe three shorts in the anthology are titled \"Hidamari no Choushoku\" (Sunny Breakfast), \"Chiisana Fashion Show\" (A Small Fashion Show), and \"Shanghai Koi\" (Shanghai Love), and all three will be set in three different Chinese cities. \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nThe theme of the three stories are food, clothing, and shelter. \"Hidamari no Choushoku\" is about a youth working in Beijing and a grandmother in his hometown. \"Chiisana Fashion Show\" is about sisters living in Guangzhou. \"Shanghai Koi\" is set in 1990s Shanghai and is a homage to Byousoku 5 Centimeter (5 Centimeters Per Second).","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":4,"month":8,"year":2018},"episodes":3,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":101231,"idMal":37396,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":69,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2018,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/101231","startDate":{"day":4,"month":8,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["肆式青春","Si Shi Qing Chun","Shiki Oriori: O Sabor da Juventude"],"title":{"english":"Flavors of Youth","native":"詩季織々","romaji":"Shikioriori","userPreferred":"Shikioriori"},"trailer":{"id":"CKdOr976h3Y","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/CKdOr976h3Y/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/20791-oJEIboUcTf4o.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e44350","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx20791-yPCX5GJuMH2k.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx20791-yPCX5GJuMH2k.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx20791-yPCX5GJuMH2k.png"},"description":"The first film in a trilogy adaptation of the third route of the popular visual novel: Fate/stay night.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n10 years after the Holy Grail War—a battle waged by Masters and Servants over the wish-granting container, the Holy Grail—another war breaks out in Fuyuki City. Shirou Emiya—the adopted son of Kiritsugu Emiya, a participant of the previous Holy Grail War—is leading a peaceful life with people dear to him. Especially close to him is his underclassman Sakura Matou, who brings kindness into his otherwise lonely life. But once the Holy Grail War starts, Shirou’s peaceful life is sundered.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Aniplex of America)","duration":120,"endDate":{"day":14,"month":10,"year":2017},"episodes":1,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Fantasy","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":20791,"idMal":25537,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2017,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/20791","startDate":{"day":14,"month":10,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Fate/HF","Судьба/Ночь схватки: Прикосновение небес"],"title":{"english":"Fate/stay night [Heaven's Feel] I. presage flower","native":"Fate/stay night[Heaven's Feel] Ⅰ.presage flower","romaji":"Fate/stay night [Heaven's Feel] I. presage flower","userPreferred":"Fate/stay night [Heaven's Feel] I. presage flower"},"trailer":{"id":"AMr5pXzpvP0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/AMr5pXzpvP0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}],"pageInfo":{"currentPage":1,"hasNextPage":true,"lastPage":250,"perPage":20,"total":5000}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-07T01:01:23.498181+03:00"},"{\"query\":\"query ListAnime ($page: Int, $search: String, $perPage: Int, $sort: [MediaSort], $status: [MediaStatus], $genres: [String], $averageScore_greater: Int, $season: MediaSeason, $seasonYear: Int, $format: MediaFormat, $isAdult: Boolean) {\\n\\tPage(page: $page, perPage: $perPage) {\\n\\t\\tpageInfo {\\n\\t\\t\\thasNextPage\\n\\t\\t\\ttotal\\n\\t\\t\\tperPage\\n\\t\\t\\tcurrentPage\\n\\t\\t\\tlastPage\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t\\tmedia(type: ANIME, search: $search, sort: $sort, status_in: $status, isAdult: $isAdult, format: $format, genre_in: $genres, averageScore_greater: $averageScore_greater, season: $season, seasonYear: $seasonYear, format_not: MUSIC) {\\n\\t\\t\\t... baseAnime\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t}\\n}\\nfragment baseAnime on Media {\\n\\tid\\n\\tidMal\\n\\tsiteUrl\\n\\tstatus(version: 2)\\n\\tseason\\n\\ttype\\n\\tformat\\n\\tseasonYear\\n\\tbannerImage\\n\\tepisodes\\n\\tsynonyms\\n\\tisAdult\\n\\tcountryOfOrigin\\n\\tmeanScore\\n\\tdescription\\n\\tgenres\\n\\tduration\\n\\ttrailer {\\n\\t\\tid\\n\\t\\tsite\\n\\t\\tthumbnail\\n\\t}\\n\\ttitle {\\n\\t\\tuserPreferred\\n\\t\\tromaji\\n\\t\\tenglish\\n\\t\\tnative\\n\\t}\\n\\tcoverImage {\\n\\t\\textraLarge\\n\\t\\tlarge\\n\\t\\tmedium\\n\\t\\tcolor\\n\\t}\\n\\tstartDate {\\n\\t\\tyear\\n\\t\\tmonth\\n\\t\\tday\\n\\t}\\n\\tendDate {\\n\\t\\tyear\\n\\t\\tmonth\\n\\t\\tday\\n\\t}\\n\\tnextAiringEpisode {\\n\\t\\tairingAt\\n\\t\\ttimeUntilAiring\\n\\t\\tepisode\\n\\t}\\n}\\n\",\"variables\":{\"isAdult\":false,\"page\":1,\"perPage\":20,\"season\":\"FALL\",\"seasonYear\":2025,\"sort\":[\"SCORE_DESC\"]}}":{"value":{"Page":{"media":[{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/182896-iJt79hYTpv8w.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#c9d6f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx182896-mvxTVHGdDB4q.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx182896-mvxTVHGdDB4q.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx182896-mvxTVHGdDB4q.jpg"},"description":"The eighth and final season of \u003ci\u003eBoku no Hero Academia\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nDeku and the heroes are plunged into a final battle against villains across Japan. Deku, by fully unleashing One For All Quirks, faces off against Shigaraki. A young and refreshed All For One faces Armored All Might, Quirkless in his powered armor suit. Will Deku be able to bring the story of how they all became the greatest heroes to its finale? Or will everything be destroyed?!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":23,"endDate":{"day":13,"month":12,"year":2025},"episodes":11,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure"],"id":182896,"idMal":60098,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":87,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2025,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/182896","startDate":{"day":4,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Boku no Hero Academia 8","My Hero Academia 8","BNHA 8","MHA 8","Моя геройская академия 8","ヒロアカ 8","มายฮีโร่ อคาเดเมีย ไฟนอลซีซัน"],"title":{"english":"My Hero Academia FINAL SEASON","native":"僕のヒーローアカデミア FINAL SEASON","romaji":"Boku no Hero Academia FINAL SEASON","userPreferred":"Boku no Hero Academia FINAL SEASON"},"trailer":{"id":"wQgQij8Ry4g","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wQgQij8Ry4g/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/195240-HcuZvXcdT5aX.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5093e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx195240-hKcmllV6YHQT.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx195240-hKcmllV6YHQT.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx195240-hKcmllV6YHQT.jpg"},"description":"The second half of \u003ci\u003eUmamusume: Cinderella Gray\u003c/i\u003e. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nHailing from the humble countryside, Oguri Cap has turned the racing world on its head. Her rampage through the national race scene seemed unstoppable... until it wasn't. Tamamo Cross, the current peak of racing, has bested the Beast and declared Oguri Cap her rival. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nBut Oguri Cap can't afford to keep her attention on Tamamo Cross alone. One by one, racers from all over the world arrive in Japan, ready to demonstrate their own prowess. Up against the best the world has to offer, our ashen racer will need to reach beyond her limits if she wants to stand a chance… Keep those eyes peeled—a Cinderella story full of twists and turns lies ahead!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: It's Anime powered by REMOW)\n","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":21,"month":12,"year":2025},"episodes":10,"format":"TV","genres":["Drama","Sports"],"id":195240,"idMal":61930,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":86,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2025,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/195240","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Umamusume: Cinderella Gray Cour 2"],"title":{"english":"Umamusume: Cinderella Gray 2nd Cour","native":"ウマ娘 シンデレラグレイ 第2クール","romaji":"Uma Musume: Cinderella Gray Part 2","userPreferred":"Uma Musume: Cinderella Gray Part 2"},"trailer":{"id":"MNZchQvbMa0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MNZchQvbMa0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/194884-PwYRWyOUEwZI.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#1a78ff","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx194884-rHgGAzKSCEWz.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx194884-rHgGAzKSCEWz.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx194884-rHgGAzKSCEWz.jpg"},"description":"TV special for \u003ci\u003eKaguya-sama wa Kokurasetai\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The anime first premiered in Japan as a TV Special, and was later split into 2 episodes on streaming.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":26,"endDate":{"day":31,"month":12,"year":2025},"episodes":2,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Comedy","Psychological","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":194884,"idMal":61903,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2025,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/194884","startDate":{"day":31,"month":12,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Kaguya-sama: Love Is War - The Grown-Up Staircase"],"title":{"english":"Kaguya-sama: Love Is War -Stairway to Adulthood-","native":"かぐや様は告らせたい 大人への階段","romaji":"Kaguya-sama wa Kokurasetai: Otona e no Kaidan","userPreferred":"Kaguya-sama wa Kokurasetai: Otona e no Kaidan"},"trailer":{"id":"LyHTqu5Yg7I","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/LyHTqu5Yg7I/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#50aee4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx190840-CvKAz6aWHB21.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx190840-CvKAz6aWHB21.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx190840-CvKAz6aWHB21.png"},"description":"The sixth season of \u003ci\u003eKingdom\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":12,"year":2025},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Action"],"id":190840,"idMal":61517,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2025,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/190840","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Царство 6"],"title":{"english":"Kingdom Season 6","native":"キングダム 第6シリーズ","romaji":"Kingdom 6th Season","userPreferred":"Kingdom 6th Season"},"trailer":{"id":"IT5EyilwgoQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IT5EyilwgoQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c9bb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b204080-VRTTOykaiNRV.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b204080-VRTTOykaiNRV.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b204080-VRTTOykaiNRV.png"},"description":"Reze dances to \u003ci\u003eIRIS OUT\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":1,"endDate":{"day":12,"month":12,"year":2025},"episodes":1,"format":"ONA","genres":[],"id":204080,"idMal":null,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":85,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2025,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/204080","startDate":{"day":12,"month":12,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["レゼダンス","Reze Dance"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"IRIS OUT","romaji":"IRIS OUT","userPreferred":"IRIS OUT"},"trailer":{"id":"o2rrJ7FDi-g","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/o2rrJ7FDi-g/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/177937-jty4x7qBWG5n.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx177937-Tzgg6rAdhCoH.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx177937-Tzgg6rAdhCoH.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx177937-Tzgg6rAdhCoH.jpg"},"description":"The third season of \u003ci\u003eSPY×FAMILY\u003c/i\u003e. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nWorld peace is at stake and secret agent Twilight must undergo his most difficult mission yet—pretend to be a family man. Posing as a loving husband and father, he’ll infiltrate an elite school to get close to a high-profile politician. He has the perfect cover, except his wife’s a deadly assassin and neither knows each other’s identity. But someone does, his adopted daughter who’s a telepath!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":27,"month":12,"year":2025},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy","Slice of Life","Supernatural"],"id":177937,"idMal":59027,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2025,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/177937","startDate":{"day":4,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["SxF 3","スパイファミリー 3","SPY×FAMILY ซีซั่น 3","SPY×FAMILY 間諜家家酒 Season 3","間諜家家酒 Season 3"],"title":{"english":"SPY x FAMILY Season 3","native":"SPY×FAMILY Season 3","romaji":"SPY×FAMILY Season 3","userPreferred":"SPY×FAMILY Season 3"},"trailer":{"id":"9-JreaprnO0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/9-JreaprnO0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/198188-rIqUa8loin9T.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4d650","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx198188-h3w6uICVNhqh.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx198188-h3w6uICVNhqh.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx198188-h3w6uICVNhqh.png"},"description":"An anthology series adapting 8 short stories created by manga artist Tatsuki Fujimoto between ages 17 and 26.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n1) \u003ci\u003eA Couple Clucking Chickens Were Still Kickin' in the Schoolyard\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Seishirou Nagaya, ZEXCS)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n2) \u003ci\u003eSasaki Stopped a Bullet\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Nobukage Kimura, Lapin Track)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n3) \u003ci\u003eLove is Blind\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Nobuyuki Takeuchi, Lapin Track)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n4) \u003ci\u003eShikaku\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Naoya Ando, GRAPH77)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n5) \u003ci\u003eMermaid Rhapsody\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Tetsuaki Watanabe, 100Studio)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n6) \u003ci\u003eWoke-Up-as-a-Girl Syndrome\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Kazuaki Terasawa, Studio Kafka)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n7) \u003ci\u003eNayuta of the Prophecy\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Tetsuaki Watanabe, 100Studio)\n\u003cbr\u003e\n8) \u003ci\u003eSisters\u003c/i\u003e (Dir. Osamu Honma, P.A.WORKS)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: This anime had a pre-release world premiere at the \"Global Stage Hollywood 2025\" film festival on October 5, 2025. A general two-week theatrical run in Japan divided into two parts released on the same day October 17, 2025. The anime series later streamed worldwide in Amazon Prime Video on November 8, 2025.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":18,"endDate":{"day":17,"month":10,"year":2025},"episodes":8,"format":"MOVIE","genres":["Action","Comedy","Drama","Romance","Sci-Fi","Slice of Life","Supernatural"],"id":198188,"idMal":62405,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2025,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/198188","startDate":{"day":17,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["A Couple Clucking Chickens Were Still Kickin' in the Schoolyard","Sasaki Stopped a Bullet","Love is Blind","Shikaku","Mermaid Rhapsody","Woke-Up-as-a-Girl Syndrome","Nayuta of the Prophecy","Sisters"," 庭には二羽 ニワトリがいた。","佐々木くんが 銃弾止めた","恋は盲目","シカク","人魚ラプソディ","目が覚めたら 女の子になっていた病 ","予言のナユタ","妹の姉"],"title":{"english":"Tatsuki Fujimoto 17-26","native":"藤本タツキ 17-26","romaji":"Fujimoto Tatsuki 17-26","userPreferred":"Fujimoto Tatsuki 17-26"},"trailer":{"id":"xDsN2cmAlhQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/xDsN2cmAlhQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/185731-LUMIdwsqtTrX.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6351a","extraLarg