ime/cover/large/bx207385-hyeDUEGGUxeV.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx207385-hyeDUEGGUxeV.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx207385-hyeDUEGGUxeV.jpg"},"description":"The sixth season of \u003ci\u003eDungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":null,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":207385,"idMal":63442,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":null,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":null,"seasonYear":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/207385","startDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"status":"NOT_YET_RELEASED","synonyms":["It Wrong To Try To Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? VI","DanMachi 6","ダンまちⅥ"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"ダンジョンに出会いを求めるのは間違っているだろうかⅤI","romaji":"Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka VI","userPreferred":"Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka VI"},"trailer":{"id":"nlQX8TyUnVY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/nlQX8TyUnVY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx169580-AVbAp5Lu07YC.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx169580-AVbAp5Lu07YC.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx169580-AVbAp5Lu07YC.jpg"},"description":"I, Maki Maehara, was the loner boy in my class, until I made my first friend, Umi Asanagi. Asanagi is always at the center of attention, and boys considered her to be \"the second cutest girl in the class.\" I thought I was just a guy in the shadows, living in a completely different world from her, but it turned out that she liked B-movies, too! Now Asanagi-san secretly comes over to my house on Fridays after school. We have a great time together, as we share the same interests in movies, games, and manga. \u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\n\"Sit next to me and we can read manga together.\"\u003cBR\u003e\n\"This is my bed.......\"\u003cBR\u003e\n\"It's my bed for now. Come on, come over here.\"\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\nIsn't that a bit too close, Asanagi-san?\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\n(Source: ComicWalker, translated)","duration":null,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":169580,"idMal":56734,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":null,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1775572200,"episode":1,"timeUntilAiring":2737717},"season":"SPRING","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/169580","startDate":{"day":7,"month":4,"year":2026},"status":"NOT_YET_RELEASED","synonyms":["I Became Friends with the Second Cutest Girl in My Class","I Made Friends with the Second Prettiest Girl in My Class"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"クラスで２番目に可愛い女の子と友だちになった","romaji":"Class de 2-banme ni Kawaii Onnanoko to Tomodachi ni Natta","userPreferred":"Class de 2-banme ni Kawaii Onnanoko to Tomodachi ni Natta"},"trailer":{"id":"NCE8HDUpCeU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/NCE8HDUpCeU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4d628","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx204356-1in4XnaKX9n0.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx204356-1in4XnaKX9n0.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx204356-1in4XnaKX9n0.jpg"},"description":"\"More,\" a new story by Kohei Horikoshi, is being adapted into an anime! It tells the story of Deku and friends after the final episode, published in the 42nd and final volume of the original manga.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Official Website, translated)","duration":null,"endDate":{"day":2,"month":5,"