his chaos, the Jujutsu Headquarters revokes Yuji Itadori’s suspended death sentence and appoints special-grade sorcerer Yuta Okkotsu as his executioner. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nNewly awakened modern sorcerers and resurrected ancient ones,  now fighting as players in the Culling Game, collide with conflicting motives, driving the world once more toward an age ruled by jujutsu.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: TOHO Animation)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":27,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Drama","Supernatural"],"id":172463,"idMal":57658,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773329160,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":495771},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/172463","startDate":{"day":9,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Jujutsu Kaisen 3rd Season","呪術廻戦 第3期","JJK3","มหาเวทย์ผนึกมาร จรดลล้างบาง พาร์ต 1"],"title":{"english":"JUJUTSU KAISEN Season 3: The Culling Game Part 1","native":"呪術廻戦 死滅回游 前編","romaji":"Jujutsu Kaisen: Shimetsu Kaiyuu - Zenpen","userPreferred":"Jujutsu Kaisen: Shimetsu Kaiyuu - Zenpen"},"trailer":{"id":"ruX3rIj3--w","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ruX3rIj3--w/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-109029},{"airingAt":1772722800,"episode":2,"id":403964,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a1a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx198511-R3bEhSgsbCxr.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx198511-R3bEhSgsbCxr.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx198511-R3bEhSgsbCxr.png"},"description":"\u003cb\u003eEpisode 1\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eCostte Totte Hamete\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAfter joining the drama club, Katayama found common ground with the aloof Nishida-senpai through discussions about costume design. One night, he opened a URL sent to his phone and received photos of the senior wearing a costume designed by herself. When he was asked for his thoughts on it the next day, he was taken to the senior's house, where an erotic photo shoot began.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eKikoetemasu Seitokaichou\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nUchino joined the student council to get closer to Megumi Hokura, the student council president he admired. He was supposed to be working diligently in the student council room, but Hokura's movements right in front of him looked exactly like she was masturbating. Yet he couldn't bring himself to point it out, spending his days in agonizing frustration. When Hokura's documents fell to the floor and Uchino bent down to pick them up, a lewd sight met his eyes.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eEpisode 2\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eKurotaki Buchou no Inokori Shidou\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThe swimming club, now under a new system, was undergoing rigorous training under the leadership of Captain Kurotaki. After each practice, the captain would call in a male member, and within a week or so, that member would quit. Finally, it is my turn... Once inside the equipment room, I am ordered to take off my swimsuit and questioning begins. My flaccid cock expands in the captain's mouth as she stares at it, and my thick, erect cock becomes a sex toy to satisfy the captain's desires.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eKikkake wa Sasainakoto\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThat day, Mayu had swimming class from the first period, but she forgot her underwear. From the second period onwards, she spent the whole time without any underwear under her skirt. Realizing that she might be seen by someone and that the thrill of it might be fun, she escalates to masturbating in the bathroom during breaks and using toys after school. One day, while she was masturbating with a remote-controlled vibrator in an empty classroom, a male student came into the room. With this guy, she can have even more fun...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Mediabank, translated)","duration":20,"endDate":{"day":6,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":2,"format":"OVA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":198511,"idMal":62686,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":72,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/198511","startDate":{"day":30,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"制服は着たままで","romaji":"Seifuku wa Kita mama de","userPreferred":"Seifuku wa Kita mama de"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-110589},{"airingAt":1772722800,"episode":1,"id":403407,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/177132-0HGgOyzHq7Nx.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#43bbe4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx177132-V5P7e5f5OzNB.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx177132-V5P7e5f5OzNB.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx177132-V5P7e5f5OzNB.jpg"},"description":"The Obinata Fireworks Shop factory is getting prepared for an administrative action for confiscation tomorrow. It has been six years since Keitaro has been holed up in a closed-down factory creating fireworks by himself, chasing after an illusion of his father who vanished. It is a story about three young people who overcome the extreme weather conditions, disasters and environmental problems imposed on them and establish their own identities.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Marché  du Film Festival de Cannes)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n*\u003ci\u003eThe film was selected for the 77th Cannes Film Festival’s 2024 Annecy Animation Showcase.\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e*\u003ci\u003eNote: Initially slated for a 2025 release, on May 20th of the same year the movie was delayed to 2026. \u0