yroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":26,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":185039,"idMal":60395,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773325800,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":492411},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/185039","startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["รักใส ใจละมุน กับคุณที่มองไม่เห็น"],"title":{"english":"The Invisible Man and His Soon-to-Be Wife","native":"透明男と人間女～そのうち夫婦になるふたり～","romaji":"Toumei Otoko to Ningen Onna: Sonouchi Fuufu ni Naru Futari","userPreferred":"Toumei Otoko to Ningen Onna: Sonouchi Fuufu ni Naru Futari"},"trailer":{"id":"W1kp6GQhiOk","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/W1kp6GQhiOk/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-112389},{"airingAt":1772719200,"episode":9,"id":404774,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/176276-ES97CHqKSrLg.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1505d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx176276-rtF8mYd2OWw2.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx176276-rtF8mYd2OWw2.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx176276-rtF8mYd2OWw2.png"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eMato Seihei no Slave.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":26,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Drama","Ecchi","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":176276,"idMal":58505,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":73,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773324000,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":490611},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/176276","startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Mabotai 2","魔都精兵のスレイブ 第２期","Mato Seihei no Slave 2nd Season","ทาสสุดแกร่งแห่งหน่วยป้องกันอสูร ซีซั่น 2"],"title":{"englis