 as a cat.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Bilibili)","duration":10,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":36,"format":"ONA","genres":["Romance","Supernatural"],"id":203710,"idMal":60591,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":71,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773313200,"episode":20,"timeUntilAiring":479811},"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/203710","startDate":{"day":11,"month":11,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Just for a Meowment","Myohan Insaeng","묘한 인생"],"title":{"english":"Reborn as a Cat","native":"为喵人生","romaji":"Wei Miao Rensheng","userPreferred":"Wei Miao Rensheng"},"trailer":{"id":"5bqBtR_flBE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/5bqBtR_flBE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-124989},{"airingAt":1772708400,"episode":23,"id":405472,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e47843","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx194389-DAbj4TOj5GB9.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx194389-DAbj4TOj5GB9.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx194389-DAbj4TOj5GB9.png"},"description":"The manga is about Koala who writes about daily life, whether it's good or bad, happy or sad, Koala treats every day as a precious day. Koala believes that today is a good day, and tomorrow will be a good day too.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":2,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"ONA","genres":["Slice of Life"],"id":194389,"idMal":62005,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":55,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773313200,"episode":24,"timeUntilAiring":479811},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/194389","startDate":{"day":2,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Koala's Diary"],"title":{"english":"Koala's Diary","native":"コアラ絵日記","romaji":"Koala Enikki","userPreferred":"Koala Enikki"},"trailer":{"id":"jnSt-yJxigA","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jnSt-yJxigA/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-124989},{"airingAt":1772703000,"episode":21,"id":406785,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx199635-rgif9o9VWMrt.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx199635-rgif9o9VWMrt.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx199635-rgif9o9VWMrt.png"},"description":"The stage moves from the Mysterious Amusement Park to the \"Strange Paradise,\" where our friends from season 1, PetitCure Mofurun and PetitCure Pollun, will meet new allies like PetitCure Niko and PetitCure Candy!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nIn a Strange Paradise entirely made up of sweets, everyone goes on a candy-eating spree!? Many more heartwarming and cute PetitCure stories that'll make you smile and feel all warm inside await ♡ \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n (Source: Official Website News, translated, edited)","duration":null,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"ONA","genres":["Fantasy","Slice of Life"],"id":199635,"idMal":62676,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773307800,"episode":22,"timeUntilAiring":474411},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/199635","startDate":{"day":9,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["PuchiCure 2"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"ぷちきゅあ～Precure Fairies～ シーズン２","romaji":"PetitCure: Precure Fairies Season 2","userPreferred":"PetitCure: Precure Fairies Season 2"},"trailer":{"id":"ld_1kgxUa08","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ld_1kgxUa08/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-130389},{"airingAt":1772661600,"episode":9,"id":407145,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f15d93","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx205676-VlzcdwHYdJCe.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx205676-VlzcdwHYdJCe.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx205676-VlzcdwHYdJCe.png"},"description":"Osamu Tezuka's classic manga \"Black Jack\" has been adapted into a comedy anime by creator SoroTani, the man behind the YouTube channel \"SoroTani no Animetchi,\" which has been viewed over 1 billion times.","duration":2,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"ONA","genres":["Comedy"],"id":205676,"idMal":63275,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":60,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773266400,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":433011},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/205676","startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"ブラックジャックやねん","romaji":"Black Jack Yanen","userPreferred":"Black Jack Yanen"},"trailer":{"id":"OkiloDdugO0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/OkiloDdugO0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-171789},{"airingAt":1772636400,"episode":10,"id":406921,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/178005-X4Tr7p0sCQbx.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f15078","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx178005-pCEReATswrup.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx178005-pCEReATswrup.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx178005-pCEReATswrup.jpg"},"description":"Utage Kinoshita is a high school girl who works part-time as a housekeeper. She has devoted her life to her favorite idol, Tamon Fukuhara, from the group F/ACE. Then one day, Utage ends up being assigned to Tamon’s house! There she discovers that off-stage, he is nothing like his wild idol persona. A gloomy, introverted boy with no self-confidence, Utage still finds herself falling for him anyway.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":26,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":13,"format":"ONA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":178005,"idMal":59047,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773241200,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":407811},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/178005","startDate":{"day":1,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Two F/aced Tamon","Which Face Does Tamon Have Now?","ทามอนคุง ตอนนี้อยู่โหมดไหน!?"],"title":{"english":"Tamon's B-Side","native":"多聞くん今どっち！？","romaji":"Tamon-kun Ima Docchi!?","userPreferred":"Tamon-kun Ima Docchi!?"},"trailer":{"id":"qFmSz2ZVxCA","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qFmSz2ZVxCA/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-196989},{"airingAt":1772636400,"episode":9,"id":405298,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/182771-93HQnmbLFYbE.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6c9","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx182771-KVq712ii32fJ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx182771-KVq712ii32fJ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx182771-KVq712ii32fJ.jpg"},"description":"Lizel, a brilliant young chancellor of a powerful nation in a fantasy realm, suddenly finds himself transported to another world—mid-conversation, no less. Unfazed, he decides to treat it like a vacation and become an adventurer! Teaming up with Gil, a lone wolf top-ranker, Lizel uses his wit, charm, and intellect to navigate this new world. So begin the whimsical adventures of a noble off duty!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Fantasy","Slice of Life"],"id":182771,"idMal":60071,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":65,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773241200,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":407811},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/182771","startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["A Mild Noble's Vacation Suggestion"],"title":{"english":"A Gentle Noble's Vacation Recommendation","native":"穏やか貴族の休暇のすすめ。","romaji":"Odayaka Kizoku no Kyuuka no Susume.","userPreferred":"Odayaka Kizoku no Kyuuka no Susume."},"trailer":{"id":"LKlXRCtlOVY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/LKlXRCtlOVY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-196989},{"airingAt":1772636400,"episode":10,"id":405037,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e49350","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187264-aOUNQvTriPkX.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187264-aOUNQvTriPkX.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187264-aOUNQvTriPkX.jpg"},"description":"Betrayed by his childhood friend and cast out of the Hero Party, Orhun Dura—once their loyal Enchanter—is branded by his former comrades as “a jack-of-all-trades but a master of none.” Alone, he sets out to forge a new path as a solo adventurer. His journey sparks explosive battles, deadly rivals, and unexpected allies—and he’ll rise to shatter every expectation. The ultimate solo comeback begins!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":12,"format":"ONA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":187264,"idMal":61128,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":66,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773241200,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":407811},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187264","startDate":{"day":