rImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/180746-AyfiOMkuHegF.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#50c9fe","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx180746-eqDiHbzoHMFh.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx180746-eqDiHbzoHMFh.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx180746-eqDiHbzoHMFh.jpg"},"description":"At just seventeen, Yuki is a professional death game player. She’s survived enough rounds to know that survival is calculation, not luck—and that failure is final. For most players, the games are a nightmare with no escape. For Yuki, they’re simply business. Yet in a world where rooms turn into graves and every choice could be her last, even experience offers no protection.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The first episode aired with a runtime of ~47 minutes as opposed to the standard 24 minute long episode.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":18,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":11,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Drama","Mystery","Thriller"],"id":180746,"idMal":59711,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":75,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773239400,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":406011},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/180746","startDate":{"day":7,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["SHIBOYUGI: Jogos Mortais para Colocar Comida na Mesa","SHIBOYUGI: Juegos mortales para ganarse el pan","SHIBOYUGI: Das Phantom-Mädchen im Spiel des Todes","Смертельная игра ради еды на столе","Смертельні ігри заради їжі на столі","Kiếm Cơm Bằng Trò Chơi Sinh Tử","靠死亡游戏混饭吃。","ลิขิตชะตาเกมท้าตาย","SHIBOYUGI : Survivre est mon métier","사망 유희로 밥을 먹는다."],"title":{"english":"SHIBOYUGI: Playing Death Games to Put Food on the Table","native":"死亡遊戯で飯を食う。","romaji":"Shibou Yuugi de Meshi wo Kuu.","userPreferred":"Shibou Yuugi de Meshi wo Kuu."},"trailer":{"id":"rqp_JkzslnM","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rqp_JkzslnM/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-198789},{"airingAt":1772632800,"episode":8,"id":406212,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/182587-SLNmuinewbUF.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45df1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx182587-fsU8LOjmd7oj.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx182587-fsU8LOjmd7oj.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx182587-fsU8LOjmd7oj.jpg"},"description":"The third season of \u003ci\u003e[Oshi no Ko]\u003c/i\u003e.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThe story enters a new stage.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nIt's been six months since \"POP IN 2\" was released. Thanks to MEM-Cho's hard work, B-Komachi is about to get their major break. Aqua is a multi-talented entertainer, and Akane's career as a talented actress is going smoothly. Meanwhile, Kana lost the cheerfulness she once had. To track down the truth behind Ai and Goro's deaths, Ruby keeps rising in the entertainment world...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eUsing lies as a weapon.\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":11,"format":"TV","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":182587,"idMal":60058,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773237600,"episode":9,"timeUntilAiring":404211},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/182587","startDate":{"day":14,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["[OSHI NO KO] Season 3"],"title":{"english":"【OSHI NO KO】Season 3","native":"【推しの子】第3期","romaji":"[Oshi no Ko] 3rd Season","userPreferred":"[Oshi no Ko] 3rd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"JGYY6Pui5Kc","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JGYY6Pui5Kc/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-200589},{"airingAt":1772629200,"episode":9,"id":404877,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/191205-1ZMdtwrP4ClU.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#a1c9e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx191205-ALhucRyrwOW1.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx191205-ALhucRyrwOW1.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx191205-ALhucRyrwOW1.jpg"},"description":"Van, fourth son of a marquis, is just a toddler when he realizes he’s been reincarnated. Thanks to his literal lifetime of knowledge, he’s raised as a child prodigy—until his production magic manifests, and it’s the last thing his snooty mage family wants to see! His disappointed father banishes him to a podunk town on the verge of collapse, yet Van can only see the place’s potential. Can our hero’s bastion of battlements build a better life than battle magic ever could?!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"ONA","genres":["Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":191205,"idMal":61549,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773234000,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":400611},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/191205","startDate":{"day":7,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["หนูน้อยเจ้าแคว้นกับแผนพิทักษ์เมือง เปลี่ยนเมืองไร้ชื่อให้กลายเป็นนครป้อมปราการด้วยเวทมนตร์การผลิต"],"title":{"english":"Easygoing Territory Defense by the Optimistic Lord","native":"お気楽領主の楽しい領地防衛","romaji":"Okiraku Ryoushu no Tanoshii Ryouchi Bouei","userPreferred":"Okiraku Ryoushu no Tanoshii Ryouchi Bouei"},"trailer":{"id":"-lgT3jToqOI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-lgT3jToqOI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-204189},{"airingAt":1772627400,"episode":9,"id":404927,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/192261-ccBYYYrlx24B.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#bbe4f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx192261-oaqwOjlr64ki.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx192261-oaqwOjlr64ki.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx192261-oaqwOjlr64ki.jpg"},"description":"Having spent his childhood in the slums, Hajime Shinonome desperately sought strength to survive.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nNow, he enjoys a peaceful and carefree life as a resident adventurer of the Komai Village.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nOne day, during a quest, he ventured into a dungeon and finds a young girl being partially eaten by a weakest kind of monster, a slime!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThe girl's name was Lirui. Having been abandoned by her parents, she had no place to go and entered the dungeon alone in order to stay alive. Hajime couldn't just leave her there, so he took her back to the village to live with him!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Fantasy","Slice of Life"],"id":192261,"idMal":61637,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":58,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773232200,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":398811},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/192261","startDate":{"day":7,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Everyday of the 29 years old single person adventurer.","The Everyday Life of a 29-Year Old Middling Adventurer","The Daily Life of a Single 29-Year-Old Adventurer","ชีวิตประจำวันของนักผจญภัยโสดวัย 29"],"title":{"english":"An Adventurer’s Daily Grind at Age 29","native":"29歳独身中堅冒険者の日常","romaji":"29-sai Dokushin Chuuken Boukensha no Nichijou","userPreferred":"29-sai Dokushin Chuuken Boukensha no Nichijou"},"trailer":{"id":"_htCsAG0hUo","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/_htCsAG0hUo/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-205989},{"airingAt":1772622000,"episode":21,"id":409242,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e46b5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx188529-6o9byjahRpEx.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx188529-6o9byjahRpEx.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx188529-6o9byjahRpEx.jpg"},"description":"What if cats appeared in that story…? When beloved old tales and fairy stories are joined by cats, a surreal and heartwarming new adventure begins…!? Tabby cats, orange cats, calico cats, and white cats— a delightful mix of feline friends woven into timeless stories is sure to soothe the hearts of all humanity! A charming cat comedy is about to unfold!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: AniOne Asia)","duration":3,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"ONA","genres":["Comedy"],"id":188529,"idMal":61254,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":64,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773226800,"episode":22,"timeUntilAiring":393411},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/188529","startDate":{"day":15,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Move! Cat Folktales","ขยับแล้ว! นิทานก่อนนอนกับเจ้าเหมียว"],"title":{"english":"Cat Tales","native":"うごく！ねこむかしばなし","romaji":"Ugoku! Neko Mukashi Banashi","userPreferred":"Ugoku! Neko Mukashi Banashi"},"trailer":{"id":"n-jg8syMe08","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/n-jg8syMe08/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-211389},{"airingAt":1772589600,"episode":151,"id":408201,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/137671-Ifs5ZdWoDusy.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"CN","coverImage":{"color":"#e4c9a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx137671-PzYKwpStSLIF.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx137671-PzYKwpStSLIF.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx137671-PzYKwpStSLIF.png"},"description":"The story took the nine dragons and the coffin as an introduction and brought out a huge world of primeval ages. Climbing the sky road, and singing songs, to see how Ye Fan shrouding the heavens.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Webnovel)","duration":22,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":156,"format":"ONA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Sci-Fi"],"id":137671,"idMal":51289,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773194400,"episode":152,"timeUntilAiring":361011},"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/137671","startDate":{"day":3,"month":5,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Shrounding the Heavens"],"title":{"english":"Shrouding the Heavens","native":"遮天","romaji":"Zhe Tian","userPreferred":"Zhe Tian"},"trailer":{"id":"a0N7s4OB0jA","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/a0N7s4OB0jA/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-243789},{"airingAt":1772585640,"episode":7,"id":406311,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c95d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx204698-6v7aAq92mKFl.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx204698-6v7aAq92mKFl.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx204698-6v7aAq92mKFl.png"},"description":"Anime based on industrial company Taica's mascot Gelpiyo.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nIn the story, Gelpiyo and similar characters contain the \"Alpha Gel\" quality that allow them to bounce back after any setback. They are sent out by Alpha Industry to the mysterious Geltown to further the company's plot of world domination. There, they plan to raise trouble, even though they constantly get involved in events in the town.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":4,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV_SHORT","genres":["Comedy"],"id":204698,"idMal":63216,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":30,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773190440,"episode":8,"timeUntilAiring":357051},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/204698","startDate":{"day":21,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"ゲルぴよ","romaji":"GelPiyo","userPreferred":"GelPiyo"},"trailer":{"id":"21RP0XW0nD4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/21RP0XW0nD4/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-247749},{"airingAt":1772578800,"episode":9,"id":407073,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/204656-ECYkRJKBxTLj.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#c9e443","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b204656-KXjxVB4bBhl8.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b204656-KXjxVB4bBhl8.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b204656-KXjxVB4bBhl8.jpg"},"description":"Shark Meow is an orange tabby kitty who wears a shark suit.\u003cbr\u003e\nA little clumsy and always taking things at their own cozy pace,\u003cbr\u003e\nbut every day with their best kitty friends — and the rescued baby kitty, Little Meow —\u003cbr\u003e\nis filled with unexpected little mishaps and sweet adventures.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n \nA sunny warm spot in the park, the sparkle of the sea,\u003cbr\u003e\nsteam rising from freshly roasted sweet potatoes,\u003cbr\u003e\nthe fluttery feeling of the first snowfall…\u003cbr\u003e\nThese small everyday moments fill their world with warmth and delight.\n \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nYou can’t help but smile and think, “So true!”\u003cbr\u003e\nA soft and snuggly kitty anime that brings joy to everyday moments.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: QTORY Channel)","duration":1,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"ONA","genres":["Slice of Life"],"id":204656,"idMal":63151,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":68,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773183600,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":350211},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/204656","startDate":{"day":22,"month":12,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["mofusand the animation"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"mofusand ","romaji":"mofusand","userPreferred":"mofusand"},"trailer":{"id":"Svh_xgdMWlU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Svh_xgdMWlU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-254589},{"airingAt":1772575560,"episode":36,"id":397390,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1ae43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx193883-Im5tNHwtfAmz.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx193883-Im5tNHwtfAmz.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx193883-Im5tNHwtfAmz.jpg"},"description":"Sequel to \u003ci\u003eChibi Godzilla no Gyakushuu 2\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":3,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV_SHORT","genres":["Comedy","Fantasy"],"id":193883,"idMal":61765,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773180360,"episode":37,"timeUntilAiring":346971},"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/193883","startDate":{"day":2,"month":7,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Chibi Godzilla no Gyakushuu 2025","Chibi Gojira no Gyakushuu 3"],"title":{"english":"Chibi Godzilla Raids Again Season 3","native":"ちびゴジラの逆襲(第3期)","romaji":"Chibi Godzilla no Gyakushuu 3","userPreferred":"Chibi Godzilla no Gyakushuu 3"},"trailer":{"id":"ki-dtolF7wY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ki-dtolF7wY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-257829},{"airingAt":1772575200,"episode":21,"id":407134,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#fff100","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx199931-EhQ6yMCbEvik.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx199931-EhQ6yMCbEvik.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx199931-EhQ6yMCbEvik.png"},"description":"Second season of \u003ci\u003eDokodemo Makibao \u003c/i\u003e","duration":4,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"ONA","genres":["Comedy","Sports"],"id":199931,"idMal":62662,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":46,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773180000,"episode":22,"timeUntilAiring":346611},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/199931","startDate":{"day":8,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"どこでもマキバオー ～ワールドツアー～","romaji":"Dokodemo Makibao: World Tour","userPreferred":"Dokodemo Makibao: World Tour"},"trailer":{"id":"Q5cECzU3p7g","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Q5cECzU3p7g/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-258189},{"airingAt":1772555340,"episode":9,"id":403784,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/183984-98y2n8KEQfpZ.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx183984-uq5scAXrhEdx.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx183984-uq5scAXrhEdx.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx183984-uq5scAXrhEdx.jpg"},"description":"Arne Neuntöte is a vampire detective who manipulates supernatural powers. Lynn Reinweiß is a nobleman’s daughter who loves vampires. Their worlds should never have crossed, but they join hands to solve a bloody mystery.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nIn the darkest of nights, Lynn finds herself in desperate need of help. Then she wanders into the mysterious city of \"Lügenberg\", where non-humans live. Lynn's world changes drastically when she encounters \"Arne\", a vampire who is called \"the worst\" in the city. And tonight, a new \"murder case\" has occurred. What is the truth behind the bizarre incidents that take place in a world where humanity and the bizarre intersect?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003e\"Come on, human. You may dance merrily under the crimson moon.”\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: The Case Book of Arne Steam page)","duration":23,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Mystery"],"id":183984,"idMal":60255,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":59,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773160140,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":326751},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/183984","startDate":{"day":7,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"The Case Book of Arne","native":"アルネの事件簿","romaji":"Arne no Jikenbo","userPreferred":"Arne no Jikenbo"},"trailer":{"id":"6zVNs7xRtg4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/6zVNs7xRtg4/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-278049},{"airingAt":1772550000,"episode":9,"id":405195,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/177679-9prv8e9LblMw.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#1a436b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx177679-BgsgE0fQk3qN.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx177679-BgsgE0fQk3qN.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx177679-BgsgE0fQk3qN.jpg"},"description":"Created in a biological science lab, Charlie is a half human, half chimpanzee hybrid known as a \"Humanzee\". Raised by his adoptive human parents, Charlie is now 15 and starting high school. There he meets Lucy, a clever loner who becomes his first-ever friend. But his “normal” life is shattered when the animal rights extremists who freed his mother from the lab fifteen years ago reemerge as terrorists bent on kidnapping Charlie at all costs.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kodansha USA) ","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Sci-Fi","Thriller"],"id":177679,"idMal":58886,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":65,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773154800,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":321411},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/177679","startDate":{"day":7,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Incydent Darwina","ดาร์วิน พันธุ์อุบัติใหม่"],"title":{"english":"The Darwin Incident","native":"ダーウィン事変","romaji":"Darwin Jihen","userPreferred":"Darwin Jihen"},"trailer":{"id":"zRann2zoXx0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/zRann2zoXx0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-283389},{"airingAt":1772548200,"episode":9,"id":406977,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4781a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx194318-V3STmm4wutVQ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx194318-V3STmm4wutVQ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx194318-V3STmm4wutVQ.jpg"},"description":"The Demon World once plunged the Human World into terror. With the seal broken and hordes of Demon Soldiers launching an invasion, five young warriors rushed to humanity's rescue. They were called the Samurai Troopers, and now their battle begins anew!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":24,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Sci-Fi"],"id":194318,"idMal":61830,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":58,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773153000,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":319611},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/194318","startDate":{"day":6,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["ตำนานใหม่ ซามูไรทรูปเปอร์"],"title":{"english":"Yoroi-Shinden Samurai Troopers","native":"鎧真伝サムライトルーパー","romaji":"Yoroi Shinden Samurai Troopers","userPreferred":"Yoroi Shinden Samurai Troopers"},"trailer":{"id":"loJ05nefclc","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/loJ05nefclc/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-285189},{"airingAt":1772546400,"episode":9,"id":407060,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/195515-JYI8JvJvDSZp.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bb50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx195515-p1nD71Hmr4ly.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx195515-p1nD71Hmr4ly.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx195515-p1nD71Hmr4ly.jpg"},"description":"Reincarnated as a mid-tier demon, Youki had one job: Crush the hero’s party. Then he saw the party’s priestess, Cecilia, and fell for her hard. Now this lovestruck demon vows to confess his feelings, even if it means betraying the Demon King. Will love bloom between these two sworn enemies?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":31,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Comedy","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":195515,"idMal":61983,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":62,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773151200,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":317811},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/195515","startDate":{"day":6,"month":1,"y