s sharing the same secret: They’re vampires, hiding their murky pasts. When Sooha, a female student who hates vampires, transfers to the academy, the boys find themselves irresistibly drawn to her. As strange events shake the city, old sins and buried secrets resurface, and their world begins to fracture.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Supernatural"],"id":181443,"idMal":59853,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":64,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773414000,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":579418},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/181443","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["DARK MOON: 달의 제단","DARK MOON: Darui Jedan","DARK MOON: THE BLOOD ALTAR with ENHYPEN","DARK MOON: แท่นบูชาพระจันทร์"],"title":{"english":"DARK MOON: THE BLOOD ALTAR","native":"DARK MOON　-黒の月: 月の祭壇-","romaji":"DARK MOON: Kuro no Tsuki - Tsuki no Saidan","userPreferred":"DARK MOON: Kuro no Tsuki - Tsuki no Saidan"},"trailer":{"id":"uPlPWMb-GO0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/uPlPWMb-GO0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-25382},{"airingAt":1772807400,"episode":9,"id":407178,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/200556-vp7XJGhTNK6j.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#00feff","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx200556-TezRfCQCFLbA.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx200556-TezRfCQCFLbA.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx200556-TezRfCQCFLbA.png"},"description":"The wildly eccentric group, the Kimengumi, returns in the Reiwa era with their ultra-high-energy youth comedy!","duration":23,"endDate":{"day":27,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":200556,"idMal":62804,"is