e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The first episode aired with a runtime of ~47 minutes as opposed to the standard 24 minute long episode.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":18,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":11,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Drama","Mystery","Thriller"],"id":180746,"idMal":59711,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":75,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773239400,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":404818},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/180746","startDate":{"day":7,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["SHIBOYUGI: Jogos Mortais para Colocar Comida na Mesa","SHIBOYUGI: Juegos mortales para ganarse el pan","SHIBOYUGI: Das Phantom-Mädchen im Spiel des Todes","Смертельная игра ради еды на столе","Смертельні ігри заради їжі на столі","Kiếm Cơm Bằng Trò Chơi Sinh Tử","靠死亡游戏混饭吃。","ลิขิตชะตาเกมท้าตาย","SHIBOYUGI : Survivre est mon métier","사망 유희로 밥을 먹는다."],"title":{"english":"SHIBOYUGI: Playing Death Games to Put Food on the Table","native":"死亡遊戯で飯を食う。","romaji":"Shibou Yuugi de Meshi wo Kuu.","userPreferred":"Shibou Yuugi de Meshi wo Kuu."},"trailer":{"id":"rqp_JkzslnM","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rqp_JkzslnM/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-199982},{"airingAt":1772632800,"episode":8,"id":406212,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/182587-SLNmuinewbUF.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45df1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx182587-fsU8LOjmd7oj.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx182587-fsU8LOjmd7oj.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx182587-fsU8LOjmd7oj.jpg"},"description":"The third season of \u003ci\u003e[Oshi no Ko]\u003c/i\u003e.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThe story enters a new stage.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nIt's been six months since \"POP IN 2\" was released. Thanks to MEM-Cho's hard work, B-Komachi is about to get their major break. Aqua is a multi-talented entertainer, and Akane's career as a talented actress is going smoothly. Meanwhile, Kana lost the cheerfulness she once had. To track down the truth behind Ai and Goro's deaths, Ruby keeps rising in the entertainment world...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eUsing lies as a weapon.\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":11,"format":"TV","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":182587,"idMal":60058,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773237600,"episode":9,"timeUntilAiring":403018},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/182587","startDate":{"day":14,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["[OSHI NO KO] Season 3"],"title":{"english":"【OSHI NO KO】Season 3","native":"【推しの子】第3期","romaji":"[Oshi no Ko] 3rd Season","userPreferred":"[Oshi no Ko] 3rd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"JGYY6Pui5Kc","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JGYY6Pui5Kc/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-201782},{"airingAt":1772629200,"episode":9,"id":404877,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/191205-1ZMdtwrP4ClU.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#a1c9e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx191205-ALhucRyrwOW1.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx191205-ALhucRyrwOW1.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx191205-ALhucRyrwOW1.jpg"},"description":"Van, fourth son of a marquis, is just a toddler when he realizes he’s been reincarnated. Thanks to his literal lifetime of knowledge, he’s raised as a child prodigy—until his production magic manifests, and it’s the last thing his snooty mage family wants to see! His disappointed father banishes him to a podunk town on the verge of collapse, yet Van can only see the place’s potential. Can our hero’s bastion of battlements build a better life than battle magic ever could?!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"ONA","genres":["Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":191205,"idMal":61549,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773234000,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":399418},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/191205","startDate":{"day":7,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["หนูน้อยเจ้าแคว้นกับแผนพิทักษ์เมือง เปลี่ยนเมืองไร้ชื่อให้กลายเป็นนครป้อมปราการด้วยเวทมนตร์การผลิต"],"title":{"english":"Easygoing Territory Defense by the Optimistic Lord","native":"お気楽領主の楽しい領地防衛","romaji":"Okiraku Ryoushu no Tanoshii Ryouchi Bouei","userPreferred":"Okiraku Ryoushu no Tanoshii Ryouchi Bouei"},"trailer":{"id":"-lgT3jToqOI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-lgT3jToqOI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-205382},{"airingAt":1772627400,"episode":9,"id":404927,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/192261-ccBYYYrlx24B.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#bbe4f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx192261-oaqwOjlr64ki.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx192261-oaqwOjlr64ki.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx192261-oaqwOjlr64ki.jpg"},"description":"Having spent his childhood in the slums, Hajime Shinonome desperately sought strength to survive.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nNow, he enjoys a peaceful and carefree life as a resident adventurer of the Komai Village.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nOne day, during a quest, he ventured into a dungeon and finds a young girl being partially eaten by a weakest kind of monster, a slime!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThe girl's name was Lirui. Having been abandoned by her parents, she had no place to go and entered the dungeon alone in order to stay alive. Hajime couldn't just leave her there, so he took her back to the village to live with him!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Fantasy","Slice of Life"],"id":192261,"idMal":61637,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":58,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773232200,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":397618},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/192261","startDate":{"day":7,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Everyday of the 29 years old single person adventurer.","The Everyday Life of a 29-Year Old Middling Adventurer","The Daily Life of a Single 29-Year-Old Adventurer","ชีวิตประจำวันของนักผจญภัยโสดวัย 29"],"title":{"english":"An Adventurer’s Daily Grind at Age 29","native":"29歳独身中堅冒険者の日常","romaji":"29-sai Dokushin Chuuken Boukensha no Nichijou","userPreferred":"29-sai Dokushin Chuuken Boukensha no Nichijou"},"trailer":{"id":"_htCsAG0hUo","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/_htCsAG0hUo/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-207182},{"airingAt":1772622000,"episode":21,"id":409242,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e46b5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx188529-6o9byjahRpEx.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx188529-6o9byjahRpEx.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx188529-6o9byjahRpEx.jpg"},"description":"What if cats appeared in that story…? When beloved old tales and fairy stories are joined by cats, a surreal and heartwarming new adventure begins…!? Tabby cats, orange cats, calico cats, and white cats— a delightful mix of feline friends woven into timeless stories is sure to soothe the hearts of all humanity! A charming cat comedy is about to unfold!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: AniOne Asia)","duration":3,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"ONA","genres":["Comedy"],"id":188529,"idMal":61254,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":64,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773226800,"episode":22,"timeUntilAiring":392218},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/188529","startDate":{"day":15,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Move! Cat Folktales","ขยับแล้ว! นิทานก่อนนอนกับเจ้าเหมียว"],"title":{"english":"Cat Tales","native":"うごく！ねこむかしばなし","romaji":"Ugoku! Neko Mukashi Banashi","userPreferred":"Ugoku! Neko Mukashi Banashi"},"trailer":{"id":"n-jg8syMe08","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/n-jg8syMe08/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-212582},{"airingAt":1772589600,"episode":151,"id":408201,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/137671-Ifs5ZdWoDusy.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"CN","coverImage":{"color":"#e4c9a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx137671-PzYKwpStSLIF.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx137671-PzYKwpStSLIF.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx137671-PzYKwpStSLIF.png"},"description":"The story took the nine dragons and the coffin as an introduction and brought out a huge world of primeval ages. Climbing the sky road, and singing songs, to see how Ye Fan shrouding the heavens.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Webnovel)","duration":22,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":156,"format":"ONA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Sci-Fi"],"id":137671,"idMal":51289,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773194400,"episode":152,"timeUntilAiring":359818},"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/137671","startDate":{"day":3,"month":5,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Shrounding the Heavens"],"title":{"english":"Shrouding the Heavens","native":"遮天","romaji":"Zhe Tian","userPreferred":"Zhe Tian"},"trailer":{"id":"a0N7s4OB0jA","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/a0N7s4OB0jA/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-244982},{"airingAt":1772585640,"episode":7,"id":406311,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c95d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx204698-6v7aAq92mKFl.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx204698-6v7aAq92mKFl.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx204698-6v7aAq92mKFl.png"},"description":"Anime based on industrial company Taica's mascot Gelpiyo.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nIn the story, Gelpiyo and similar characters contain the \"Alpha Gel\" quality that allow them to bounce back after any setback. They are sent out by Alpha Industry to the mysterious Geltown to further the company's plot of world domination. There, they plan to raise trouble, even though they constantly get involved in events in the town.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)","duration":4,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV_SHORT","genres":["Comedy"],"id":204698,"idMal":63216,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":30,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773190440,"episode":8,"timeUntilAiring":355858},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/204698","startDate":{"day":21,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"ゲルぴよ","romaji":"GelPiyo","userPreferred":"GelPiyo"},"trailer":{"id":"21RP0XW0nD4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/21RP0XW0nD4/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-248942},{"airingAt":1772578800,"episode":9,"id":407073,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/204656-ECYkRJKBxTLj.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#c9e443","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b204656-KXjxVB4bBhl8.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b204656-KXjxVB4bBhl8.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b204656-KXjxVB4bBhl8.jpg"},"description":"Shark Meow is an orange tabby kitty who wears a shark suit.\u003cbr\u003e\nA little clumsy and always taking things at their own cozy pace,\u003cbr\u003e\nbut every day with their best kitty friends — and the rescued baby kitty, Little Meow —\u003cbr\u003e\nis filled with unexpected little mishaps and sweet adventures.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n \nA sunny warm spot in the park, the sparkle of the sea,\u003cbr\u003e\nsteam rising from freshly roasted sweet potatoes,\u003cbr\u003e\nthe fluttery feeling of the first snowfall…\u003cbr\u003e\nThese small everyday moments fill their world with warmth and delight.\n \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nYou can’t help but smile and think, “So true!”\u003cbr\u003e\nA soft and snuggly kitty anime that brings joy to everyday moments.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: QTORY Channel)","duration":1,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"ONA","genres":["Slice of Life"],"id":204656,"idMal":63151,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":68,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773183600,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":349018},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/204656","startDate":{"day":22,"month":12,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["mofusand the animation"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"mofusand ","romaji":"mofusand","userPreferred":"mofusand"},"trailer":{"id":"Svh_xgdMWlU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Svh_xgdM